                <h4>How can I Subscribe to ChemAnalyst Services?</h4>
                <p>Clients can share their contact details by clicking on the link provided on the Home Page. Our executive will get in touch within 24 hours and initiate the subscription services. Alternatively, you can also drop a mail at <a>sales@chemanalyst.com</a></p>

                <h4>What is the Subscription Tenure and Can I Renew the Same?</h4>
                <p>The subscription tenure is one year and you can renew the same at annual intervals.</p>

                <h4>What are the Benefits of Subscribing to Platform Based Services as Data Can also Be Shared in Excel Format?</h4>
                <p>ChemAnalyst offers highly intuitive and interactive portal where you can analyse data, create and visualize pricing charts at a click of a button. It is a ‘one-stop’ where you can access historical and forecast pricing data; import/export statistics, production and demand forecast, company profiles, news & deals and other such actionable insights all on the same platform.</p>

                <h4>How Can I Check the Authenticity of the Data Published on ChemAnalyst?</h4>
                <p>ChemAnalyst relies primarily on Primary research to collect data and ensures the latest data is published at daily intervals. Our unique “Quotation Backed” pricing data ensures the authenticity of the data published.</p>

                <h4>Can I Receive a Demo before Purchasing the Subscription?</h4>
                <p>Yes, you can request for a demo before subscribing to ChemAnalyst services. For providing you a demo, we will be sending either our team to meet you personally or in case of demo from remote location, we will conduct the same through screen share. </p>

                <h4>Can I also Get a Free Trial before Purchasing the Subscription?</h4>
                <p>For selected clients, we will be providing a free trial limited on Pricing / Analysis section of the portal for one product category for a maximum of 24 hours.</p>

                <h4>Can I Subscribe to Specific Sections of the ChemAnalyst Platform?</h4>
                <p>Yes, you can select any product/s on which you can subscribe for Pricing or Analysis or Company Profiles or any Other Sections of the platform. However, we will strongly recommend subscribing for all sections of the platform for product category/ies to get the best deal. </p>

                <h4>Can I Purchase Subscription for Multiple Chemical Products on the Platform? Are there any Benefits in this Case?</h4>
                <p>Yes, you can purchase subscription for multiple products. You will get discount on our list price for purchasing subscription of multiple products together. For more details, please get in touch with our sales executive or write to sales@chemanalyst.com.</p>

                <h4>How soon I Can Get Started Once My Payment is Processed?</h4>
                <p>We can start your subscription services in less than 24 business hours post successful receipt of payment.</p>
